[[File:Temple_256.png|right]]The '''Trinsic Temple''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows recruitment of blessed units and Barons and, if upgraded, increases their recruitment speed. Placing a [[Barracks]] beside a Trinsic Temple will also increase recruitment speed.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 8

